ata-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3616739\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wkf1665702651838.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wkf1665702651838.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wkf1665702651838.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wkf1665702651838\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Minimum Value\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Minimum value allowed for the spin button widget\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wkf1665702651838__section_mjx_vwc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d748830e51\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wkf1665702651838__p_d105617e1_d105618e1_d105619e1\">This value is not mapped to the widget property.\n        Instead, it is combined with the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Maximum</span> value, and set in the ValRep\n        list as a as <var class=\"keyword varname\">Minimum</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Maximum</var> value.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wkf1665702651838__p_d105620e1_d105621e1_d105622e1\">For example, you can change the minimum and maximum\n        values of a spin button widget in Proc as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"wkf1665702651838__pre_a4q_wwc_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; set the minimum and maximum values to -16 and +16:\n$valrep(NUMFLD)=\"-15:15\" </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wkf1665702651838__p_d105623e1_d105624e1_d105625e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Increment Value</span> determines\n        the intervening points in the ValRep.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wkf1665702651838__section_wst_xwc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d748830e84\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxs1665702651483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxs1665702651483.html\" title=\"The uspinbutton widget enables the user to enter or select a numeric value by clicking a button to increase or decrease a value by a predefined interval within a predefined range. Uniface provides a logical widget called SpinButton, which is mapped to uspinbutton.\">uspinbutton (SpinButton)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ptg1665702650425.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Maximum Value</a><p>Maximum value allowed for the widget</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vyv1665702651765.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Increment Value</a><p>Amount by which the value in the spin button is increased each time it is clicked. The default is 1.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616739\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616739\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Minimum Value Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Minimum Value Minimum value allowed for the spin button widget Description This value is not mapped to the widget property. Instead, it is combined with the Maximum value, and set in the ValRep list as a as Minimum : Maximum value. For example, you can change the minimum and maximum values of a spin button widget in Proc as follows: ; set the minimum and maximum values to -16 and +16: $valrep(NUMFLD)=\"-15:15\" Copy The Increment Value determines the intervening points in the ValRep. Applies To uspinbutton (SpinButton) Related Links Maximum Value Maximum value allowed for the widget Increment Value Amount by which the value in the spin button is increased each time it is clicked. The default is 1. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}